In this article, Vice President Kamala Harris discusses various topics including equal pay, reproductive rights, climate change, gun control, and the importance of women in leadership roles. She emphasizes the need for progress and action in these areas, acknowledging the challenges and setbacks but also expressing optimism for the future. Harris also highlights the importance of coalition building and the role of the United States as a global leader in promoting gender equity and democratic values. She calls on individuals to vote and participate in shaping a more inclusive and equitable society.